Class BlipIterator<T>

  com.google.wave.api.BlipIterator<T>

public abstract class BlipIterator<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Iterator<Range>

An iterator over blip content, that consists of text or element. Please note that this iterator does not support remove operation at the moment.
